@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos(0.03)
    tmp = tmp
    v0 = (((v2 + 0.39 / tmp + 0.47) * (v2 + 0.51 * tmp + 0.20)) + ((v1 + 0.28 / v0 + 0.40) / wp.cos(v0 + 0.56)))
    v0 = v2
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.exp(v1))
